infra.name: te0722_i
infra.display: ZYNQ-7 TE0722_I. SPRT PCB: REV01, REV02
infra.description: ZYNQ-7 TE0722_I Board (form factor 1.8 x 5.1 cm) without DDR, speed grade -1 and industrial temperature range. Supported PCB Revisions: REV01,REV2. Note: Primary boot device is QSPI, SD can be used as secondary boot device only. DDR less Zynq need a modified FSBL!
